// HumanityOS Genetics, Breeding & Mutations
// Trait definitions, breeding mechanics, mutation system, and genetic diseases.
// Loaded by AssetManager, hot-reloadable.
//
// Connection to game systems:
//   Plants (data/plants.csv) -- plant traits applied to crop species
//   Creatures (data/creatures.csv) -- animal traits applied to livestock/wildlife
//   Farming system (native/src/systems/farming.rs) -- breeding and harvest use trait values
//   Skills (data/skills/skills.csv) -- skill_required references skill IDs
//   Tech tree (data/tech_tree.ron) -- advanced methods unlock via research
//   Items (data/items.csv) -- tools_required reference item IDs
//
// Inheritance model:
//   Each organism has two alleles per trait (diploid).
//   dominant: one copy expresses fully
//   recessive: two copies needed to express
//   codominant: both alleles express, blended result
//   polygenic: controlled by multiple loci, continuous distribution

